title: John Gorka - I Know
description:
John Gorka is not very well known, but is one of the best folk singer-songwriter artists I have heard in the past 20 years.

I am sharing some of his files with the goal to spread the word about this excellent artist. All of the files I am sharing I own on CD...with a signature by the artist himself.

If you go to his website you can buy his CD's directly with his signature. How many artists these days go to that trouble! http://www.johngorka.com

Anyway, just sit back and enjoy the music and if you hear what you like, support John by buying his CD's and/or catching him live.

2009.04.06

Compressed using Lame 3.93 @192 from original CD
Cover art embedded
